snippet.description:
If you play this mod somewhere else don’t forget to credit people, using the credits from the description.

I start by apologizing to all PS3 users for this re-upload and the change of plans.... A friend of mine (DropSonic) found a way to have MMFE without any need to replace your vanilla F, the install folder now its different (MMFE00001), which means you can have Project DIVA F and MMFE at the same time and also we are able to use Resolution and FPS Patches in it now.
Not forgetting that if you want resolution patches use the link on this description and the same goes for the custom songs updates and you have to create a new Save Data for MMFE.
(If you already have one MMFE save data on your PS3, you can use it)

MMFE PS3 Download Links:

- PKG Version #1:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1mlnLZFMqDVM5cunCqtLCH5Dxg-QWjPCv/view?usp=sharing
- PKG Version #2:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UY6caUQxYYdNPHEQxJClcQ5Y0Q9d-xQP/view?usp=sharing
- PKG Version #3:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jLOtn06TK_WA31wbtiyfRGecxYj7qUni/view?usp=sharing

PS3 optional UPDATES:

- Resolution and FPS patches:
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/101XgoKJDOfCFUBn1dcdGjFMQKkGomW4Q?usp=sharing
- Reversible Campaign/Melty Land Nighmatres:
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1_Ga0ifnjJ95u1jAf8b54EWKJATr2yLE5?usp=sharing

Credits:

Special Thanks for beta testers
DropSonic, luckyguy, VocalFan, Ozzy, Sal and Yukkkiii 

- All 2D edited by MikuZando;
- All AFT/M39s/F2nd/X ports made by MikuZando and Lurker;
- All charts and success scenes edited and made by MikuZando;

- MMFE Footage videos recorded by SwigS;
- Skyth for MMM and DB converter;
- Samyuu for Script Editor, UPDC and AE Template;
- korenkonder for PD Tool;
- CoolChar for helping with Project DIVA X effects order (pv_field);
- FlyingSpirits-P for the PDXHD Modules used on MMD to make poses or PVs;
- MMD Intro camera by MikuZando (me) and Ray PV camera by MikuZando (me again) and Marky;
- "Love is War" tower stage by kuroyu128;
- New Physics by feat_jinsoul, Keikei14 and Skyth;
- Loading 2D Illustrations by DrateGon;
- "BG" and "Now Loading" aet animations ported by KeiKei;
- Loadind Screenshots taken by KeiKei and Dubita;
- BG videos recorded by Dubita, MikuFan01 and Edgy-P;
- "Vocaloid in Love" and "on the rocks" new covers by beemz;
- "Dear", "Suicide Obvilion" and "Reversible Campaign" new covers by s3un6;
- "Calc" Title Screen sprite by jorj.

